626
00:31:59,839 --> 00:32:01,839
Adik Feng, kau sama seperti pahlawan.

627
00:32:02,079 --> 00:32:03,079
Kita pergi sekarang.

628
00:32:03,279 --> 00:32:03,839
Pergi.

