659
00:33:03,319 --> 00:33:04,079
siapa yang kau bilang bertele-tele?

660
00:33:04,079 --> 00:33:04,599
Aku bicara denganmu.

661
00:33:04,799 --> 00:33:05,880
Dua orang bodoh,

662
00:33:06,519 --> 00:33:07,519
atau bertarung saja?

663
00:33:08,039 --> 00:33:10,079
Mari kita lihat keributan juga

664
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:11,559
