untuk mendapatkan kekayaan besar.

698
00:34:41,639 --> 00:34:42,719
Bagaimanapun juga,

699
00:34:43,679 --> 00:34:44,679
di dalam pengadilan hari ini,

700
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:46,519
tidak ada hasil sama sekali.

701
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:50,360
Kaki Zhao Yin benar-benar patah.

702
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:53,239
